stringphp_getdns_print_json_list intvalue boolprettyPrint
This function can be used to create a JSON-formatted, "pretty printed" representation of a getdns list.

&reftitle.returnvalues;


 This function returns a character string containing the formatted list.
 NULL is returned if any conversion or memory allocation errors are encountered.
